AD_Field.Help: There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records: (1) The system requires the record for audit purposes. (2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

AD_Field.Help: There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports. There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records: (1) The system requires the record for audit purposes. (2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.
AD_Field.Description: The record is active in the system
AD_Field.Name: Active

AD_Field_Trl.Help: Hay dos métodos para que los registros no estén disponibles en el sistema: Uno es eliminar el registro; el otro es desactivarlo. Un registro desactivado no está disponible para selección; pero está disponible para Informes
AD_Field_Trl.Description: El registro está activo en el sistema
AD_Field_Trl.Name: Activo

AD_Field.Help: A Client is a company or a legal entity. You cannot share data between Clients. Tenant is a synonym for Client.
AD_Field.Name: Client

AD_Field_Trl.Help: Grupo Empresarial. No se pueden compartir datos entre diferentes grupos empresariales.
AD_Field_Trl.Name: Grupo Empresarial

AD_Field.Help: An organization is a unit of your client or legal entity - examples are store, department. You can share data between organizations.
AD_Field.Name: Organization

AD_Field_Trl.Help: Una organización es una unidad del grupo empresarial o entidad legal - Ej. Tiendas y departamentos. Es posible compartir datos entre organizaciones.
AD_Field_Trl.Description: Entidad organizacional dentro del grupo empresarial
AD_Field_Trl.Name: Organización

AD_Field.Help: A Business Partner is anyone with whom you transact. This can include Vendor, Customer, Employee or Salesperson

AD_Field_Trl.Help: Un tercero es cualquiera con quien usted realiza transacciones. Este puede incluir Proveedores, Clientes, Empleados o Vendedores.

AD_Field.Help: The Partner address indicates the location of a Business Partner
AD_Field.Description: Identifies the (ship from) address for this Business Partner
AD_Field.Name: Partner Location

AD_Field.Help: The related Business Partner Acts on behalf of the Business Partner - example the Related Partner pays invoices of the Business Partner - or we pay to the Related Partner for invoices received from the Business Partner
AD_Field.Name: Related Partner

AD_Field_Trl.Help: La relación de un tercero actua a nombre del tercero - Ejemplo: el tercero relacionado paga las facturas del tercero - o pagamos al tercero relacionado las facturas recibidas del negocio.
AD_Field_Trl.Name: Tercero Relacionado

AD_Rule.Script: import org.compiere.model.*; import org.compiere.util.*; import java.math.*; MElementValue ev = new MElementValue(A_Ctx, A_ConceptSource.getC_ElementValue_ID(), A_TrxName); String sql = "" + "SELECT Sum(iw.taxamt * CASE " + " WHEN Substr(dt.docbasetype,3,3) = 'C' " + " THEN -1 " + " ELSE 1 " + " END) AS taxamt " + "FROM lco_invoicewithholding iw " + " JOIN c_tax_acct ta " + " ON (ta.c_tax_id = iw.c_tax_id) " + " JOIN c_validcombination vc " + " ON (ta.t_credit_acct = vc.c_validcombination_id) " + " JOIN c_elementvalue ev " + " ON (vc.account_id = ev.c_elementvalue_id) " + " JOIN c_invoice i " + " ON (i.c_invoice_id = iw.c_invoice_id) " + " JOIN c_doctype dt " + " ON (i.c_doctype_id = dt.c_doctype_id) " + "WHERE i.ad_client_id = ? " + " AND iw.dateacct BETWEEN ? AND ? " + " AND i.issotrx = 'N' " + " AND iw.processed = 'Y' " + " AND iw.isactive = 'Y' " + " AND i.processed = 'Y' " + " AND i.isactive = 'Y' " + " AND ev.VALUE LIKE ? " + " AND i.c_bpartner_id = ?"; Object[] args = new Object[] { Env.getAD_Client_ID(A_Ctx), A_SendSchedule.getStartDate(), A_SendSchedule.getEndDate(), ev.getValue() + '%', A_C_BPartner_ID }; BigDecimal taxbaseamt = DB.getSQLValueBD(A_TrxName, sql, args); if (taxbaseamt != null && taxbaseamt instanceof BigDecimal) taxbaseamt.setScale(0, BigDecimal.ROUND_HALF_UP); else taxbaseamt = Env.ZERO; result = taxbaseamt;
AD_Rule.Name: Medios Magnéticos - Formato 1002 - obtener vret
